        "content": "type: document\napp_id: docs\nskill_id: document\nstatus: finished\ntitle: Berlin to Prague Trip Preparation\nfilename: Berlin_Prague_Prep_Checklist.docx\nword_count: 89\npage_count: 1\ndocx_model:\n  title: Berlin to Prague Trip Preparation\n  filename: Berlin_Prague_Prep_Checklist.docx\n  blocks[8]:\n    - type: heading\n      level: 1\n      text: \"Travel Checklist: Berlin to Prague (Summer 2026)\"\n    - type: paragraph\n      runs[1]{text}:\n        Below is a checklist based on your preferences and current 2026 travel regulations.\n    - type: heading\n      level: 2\n      text: Immediate Actions\n    - type: list\n      ordered: false\n      items[3]: Book seat reservation for July 4th (Mandatory for summer season).,Request a window seat on the left side for scenic views.,Book quiet coach reservation for the August 12th trip.\n    - type: heading\n      level: 2\n      text: Packing & Logistics\n    - type: list\n      ordered: false\n      items[4]: Prepare a packed lunch for the July 4th journey.,Download the 'Můj vlak' (ČD) or DB Navigator app for live platform updates.,Ensure you have a small amount of Czech Koruna (CZK) for local use.,Check that your ID/Passport is valid for cross-border travel.\n    - type: heading\n      level: 2\n      text: Arrival in Prague\n    - type: paragraph\n      runs[1]{text}:\n        Prague Main Station is centrally located. Use Metro Line C (Red) or the tram network to reach your accommodation.\ndocx_s3_key: chatfiles/50c1a4b9-cad1-4ea9-bc2a-fc7c616d8293/20260610_162557_6da10d63_doc_60286faa.docx.bin\nscreenshot_s3_keys:\n  \"1\": chatfiles/50c1a4b9-cad1-4ea9-bc2a-fc7c616d8293/20260610_162557_6da10d63_doc_60286faa_p1.png.bin\naes_key: VpY/et6MMFZ1p5VIUUSb91dzSHDMUVG0y/qOSsoFkE4=\naes_nonce: \"\"\nvault_wrapped_aes_key: \"vault:v1:8WCV3IYGqd9+tPldhPwqkoo/yF3dfVhmi+VYNT9UgpqFOy4E4aNeu0tDlFFH8IdGLcLGNDEsji6cYV/bt9CQYqHdHuu23Xmb\"",
